"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-sport-olympics-olympics-swimming-collapse-tamara-potocka-slovakia-paris-2024-b1174418.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport|Olympics  Slovakiaswimmer Tamara Potocka collapsed poolside Friday morning after a qualifying heat of the women's 200-metre individual medley at the ParisOlympics.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 398, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 261, \"end\": 267, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamara_Todevska\", \"score\": 0.9981439077416804, \"rank\": 0.0018444309451275634, \"text\": \"Tamara\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamara_Todevska\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamara_Todevska\"}, {\"begin\": 268, \"end\": 275, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Potocka\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Medics applied first aid before she was carried off on a stretcher in worrying scenes.\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 486, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Potocka, 21, was seen wearing an oxygen mask as she was taken away but medical personnel at the pool said she was conscious.\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 612, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 488, \"end\": 495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Potocka\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Potocka collapsed as she got out of the water and almost immediately was surrounded by a half-dozen medical attendants, who put her on a stretcher after about a minute and carried her away from the poolside.\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 821, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A report by The Athletic revealed an asthma attack was given as the initial reason behind the collapse.\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 926, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 835, \"end\": 847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Athletic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Athletic\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Athletic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Athletic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Potocka finished seventh in herswimmingheat in a time of two minutes, 14.20 seconds.\", \"from\": 928, \"to\": 1012, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her time was not fast enough to advance her to the semi-finals of the event, which eliminated her from theOlympic Games.\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1133, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK iss